{"tid":2154931,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"拜登=熱狗","createTime":"2020-08-13T12:08:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T13:17:48.000Z","uid":23758,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"07ae9ba8c04e638d4a133abce613e361fec869c6","tid":2154931,"uid":23758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T12:08:28.000Z","msg":"連登仔重回2015-2017高登水平<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由得佢地鬥啦<br />\n雖然明知熱狗9UP得把口又奶共唔做野<br />\n不過佢地口講係本土就要撐埋一份<br />\n理得佢同本民青爭票<br />\n又偽造事實又老屈對家<br />\n幾低莊都冇問題<br />\n我地香港人要買兩邊<br />\n一定唔輸得<br />\n做實事果邊輸都係抵死<br />\n<br />\n兩三年後: 光復美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好掛住侵侵呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4febf76acadc018d8707d8259ee61eac6ba257a1","tid":2154931,"uid":23758,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T13:37:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f73d029bb71b2605b6ef1abccb25b558e98ea4f","tid":2154931,"uid":23758,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T13:45:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4561b386c1d079f5c7087ce25e31a578321a5b00","tid":2154931,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T13:46:14.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"right\"><span class=\"medium\"><strong>[⇩ 美港形勢，唯一阻撓⇩]</strong></span><br />\n<span class=\"small\">- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/pAcortX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/pAcortX</a></span></p>"},{"pid":"0a20ce330a8cca821c8dfe9cc18843c6b16619fd","tid":2154931,"uid":23758,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T03:04:30.000Z","msg":"侵侵做左咁多野<br />\n香港人一句怕輸就當佢係condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就同天琦一樣"},{"pid":"f479acc764263e7d1f8199f3db23d02